STATEMENT: >>>
The current user request and current task shall have higher authority than memory, retrieved evidence, previous summaries, raw evidence, and historical context during prompt construction and interpretation.
<<<

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-SRS-NFR-SOT-005
STATUS: Draft
